{"tid":2219021,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"講真，除左王劉杜韋許，呢廿年有咩港產片係見得到下人？","createTime":"2020-09-26T14:56:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T00:55:05.000Z","uid":343680,"like":5,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"037fcaab1b2a414437d1ceaf94392f251976d410","tid":2219021,"uid":343680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T14:56:32.000Z","msg":"除左王家衛，劉鎮偉，杜琪峰，韋家輝，許鞍華<br />\n最多都係得無間道見得下人，但套戲個訊息好膚淺<br />\n狂舞派hit過下，但又係好淺<br />\n相比近既日韓，遠既歐美，就算唔係大導演，好多戲都係有意思，有訊息<br />\n睇完你會回味，有反思<br />\n但香港就真係打打打，打完就完左套戲<br />\n就算有message都真係好撚淺<br />\n<br />\n講真，真係俾班老屎忽攪灣晒<br />\n香港電影真係要改變"},{"pid":"ee39932d8c4332775a752197d98992ad76eea543","tid":2219021,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T15:00:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://topick.hket.com/article/2752412\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2752412&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0rHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=bd4204df\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://topick.hket.com/article/2752412</a>"},{"pid":"6807e84f51f2e8ce602c242c60c0b94dbf3e16ac","tid":2219021,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-26T15:01:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk01.com/電影/276905/林嶺東逝世-真正遺作-八部半-夥杜琪峯吳宇森拍出香港情\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk01.com%2F%E9%9B%BB%E5%BD%B1%2F276905%2F%E6%9E%97%E5%B6%BA%E6%9D%B1%E9%80%9D%E4%B8%96-%E7%9C%9F%E6%AD%A3%E9%81%BA%E4%BD%9C-%E5%85%AB%E9%83%A8%E5%8D%8A-%E5%A4%A5%E6%9D%9C%E7%90%AA%E5%B3%AF%E5%90%B3%E5%AE%87%E6%A3%AE%E6%8B%8D%E5%87%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%83%85&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0rHKdwoo7KeUephkEgg9e70%3D&h=fe03eb02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">hk01.com/電影/276905/林嶺東逝世-真正遺作-八部半-夥杜琪峯吳宇森拍出香港情</a>"},{"pid":"5f7c9c0ed39730e84e7ea6535d15a7e8166b254c","tid":2219021,"uid":343680,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"6807e84f51f2e8ce602c242c60c0b94dbf3e16ac","tid":2219021,"uid":370409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime